events.flavourText:
There is some sort of village in the clearing ahead. Crude stone huts have been built in a circle, smoke curling upwards from their hearths.

A large number of dog-like gnolls lounge around, drinking from rough clay mugs and enjoying the sun while conversing in low growls. They eye you warily, but make no move to approach.

scripts.text: You emerge into the forest... the sun shines above, and birds and insects can be heard nearby.
